{"tid":1938001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★零息時代勢再推高樓價　專家料樓市企穩再回升5%","createTime":"2020-03-22T09:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T09:32:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c0e60e4efbad085ef7a9753a1bf7b52b190c387a","tid":1938001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"祥益汪敦敬：樓市或成為資金避難所<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產總裁汪敦敬認為，與一月初疫情爆發時比較，目前樓市相當穩建，雖然近期經濟局勢不穩，惟放盤量有下降趨勢，反映買家未有因看淡後市而沽盤，反而認為「揸住層樓」比投資股票或做生意安全，令樓市成為資金避難所。<br />\n<br />\n他分析指，目前本港資金總供應量（M3）再創新高，可見市場資金充裕；減息現金貶值，投資者需投資新的避險資產；加上量化寬鬆後穩健、欠債少及供應有限的投資產品會被搶購，認為本港樓市結構穩建，相對其他資產較不受外圍因素影響，未來在投資市場或發展出個別「平行時空」的情況。<br />\n<br />\n雖然以往量寬皆會推動樓價，不過在失業率上升及疫情互相抵消下，認為不會出現太大升幅。而基於樓價調整、息口低企及政府放寬按揭成數，現時不少買家有能力買樓，只是政治及疫情影響而暫時「冬眠」，認為待市場恐慌情緒過後，有機會觸發樓市搶購潮，由於供應仍然短缺，料樓價繼續企穩，下半年有5%的升幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/450302/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%86%8A%E5%B8%82-%E9%9B%B6%E6%81%AF%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%8B%A2%E5%86%8D%E6%8E%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%96%99%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E4%BC%81%E7%A9%A9%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E5%8D%875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F450302%2F%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2586%258A%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E9%259B%25B6%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%258B%25A2%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25BC%2581%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%258D%25875&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=17c871d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/450302/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%86%8A%E5%B8%82-%E9%9B%B6%E6%81%AF%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%8B%A2%E5%86%8D%E6%8E%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%96%99%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E4%BC%81%E7%A9%A9%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E5%8D%875</a>"},{"pid":"9c7cbbe7e57212b9edafb849308a79b5d0f089d3","tid":1938001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6c820b509b691a045c735ed8bb0cabe6cd6169","tid":1938001,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:09:29.000Z","msg":"股巿大跌時樓價都企得穩<br />\n到股巿回穩時樓價只會升得更癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669b7a6e9ceaef532ebf03e6028a2d1819e30836","tid":1938001,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"宜家on9先會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada67fc2180fc0207aa909a67426506421e6023f","tid":1938001,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"心態好重要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1937824/page/25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1937824/page/25</a>"},{"pid":"52bc9f0f27ef4e3409ebbd2300bf2b810f74409a","tid":1938001,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c6c820b509b691a045c735ed8bb0cabe6cd6169","tid":1938001,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:09:29.000Z","msg":"股巿大跌時樓價都企得穩<br />\n到股巿回穩時樓價只會升得更癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"講到尾都係政府高樓價政策<br />\n災難級人口政策做成<br />\n呢個先入根源"},{"pid":"37ee808fb29e5e408e7086590ad13f223c7584c0","tid":1938001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c6c820b509b691